    "Name": "\"Desert Scorpion\"",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Scorpion Light Tank \"Desert Scorpion\"</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>5/8 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>125 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Scorpion tank, produced by Quikscell Company in 2807, is known for its low cost, easy repair, and availability in numbers. Known as \"The Budget Tank\", it is found on many backwater and Periphery worlds.\n\nA variant produced for the Stotzing militia, the Desert Scorpion features a 125-rated fusion engine, boosting its top speed to 84 km/h. The autocannon is replaced by a Large Laser, and an additional Machine Gun is added to the turret. For protection, the Desert Scorpion carries seven tons of armor and CASE around the machine gun ammunition.",
